data.description: MULTI-UNIT INVESTMENT PROPERTY.  This well-maintained property consists of 3 units and all units are currently occupied. Units consist of 1 2bed/2bath and 2 2bed/1bath  There is also nice shaded outdoor space.  All utilities are paid by tenants. The roof on the duplex was recently replaced and exterior painted.  Don't miss this chance to have your own income-producing property.
